                            <comment id="14524529" author="elserj" created="Sat, 2 May 2015 04:11:17 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I think I remember seeing some references to the old package (org.htrace) instead of the one for the ASF project (org.apache.htrace) in the book which could be updated as well.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
